        {
            "title": "港元拆息全線向下　短期拆息跌幅較大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港元拆息全線向下，短期拆息跌幅較大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">隔夜、1星期、2星期拆息均結束4個交易日升勢，隔夜拆息回落約28點子，跌至2.3厘以下。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">樓按相關的1個月拆息跌至2.283厘，跌約16.5點子，結束3連升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">反映銀行資金成本的3個月拆息，同樣連升3日後回軟，報2.412厘，跌約12點子。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15811316-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e5%90%91%e4%b8%8b%e3%80%80%e7%9f%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e8%bc%83%e5%a4%a7-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 12:06:32",
